Package: ProtGenesis
Type: Package
Title: Universal Protein Structure Genesis Analysis Toolkit
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-03-03
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chuanyang", "Liu", email = "example@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("ProtGenesis Analysis Team", role = "aut")
  )
Author: ProtGenesis Analysis Team
Maintainer: Chuanyang Liu <example@email.com>
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for protein structure genesis analysis
    based on the ProtGenesis framework (Liu et al., 2026). This package provides
    functions for: (1) Protein sequence generation including single-point mutations
    and stepwise truncations; (2) Building ProtGenesis objects from protein 
    language model embeddings (ProstT5, ProtT5); (3) Dimensionality reduction
    (PCA, UMAP, tSNE) for 1024D embedding visualization; (4) Clustering analysis
    using graph-based methods; (5) Spatial analysis with three novel metrics:
    Local Density (ρ), Spatial Dispersion (D), and Differential Embedding Distance (δ);
    (6) Differential embedding analysis for identifying critical mutation sites;
    (7) Multi-modal visualization including Assembly Direction Map, Genesis Path Map,
    and Status Transition Map.
